" remap za to <leader><space> to toggle folding
nmap <leader><space> za

" Mappings to navigate through ALE errors
nmap <silent> <C-t> <Plug>(ale_previous_wrap)
nmap <silent> <C-n> <Plug>(ale_next_wrap)

" Mappings for YouCompleteMe
nnoremap <silent> <leader>td :YcmCompleter GoTo<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <leader>tr :YcmCompleter GoToReferences<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <leader>tf :YcmCompleter FixIt<CR>

" Mapping for uuid generation
inoremap <c-u> <c-r>=trim(system('uuidgen'))<cr>
nnoremap <c-u> i<c-r>=trim(system('uuidgen'))<cr><esc>
